**Record Discipline**

LCES depends on disciplined record handling. That includes: • preserving chronology • versioning drafts • separating fact from conclusion • labeling materials clearly • organizing work for review, not just immediate use

The goal is not simply to generate text. The goal is to create work product that remains usable later.

